<span class="text">
G4techTV Best of CES Awards seek out the hottest new consumer technology products on the show floor. Only those products that debut at the 2005 International CES or are available for sale after December 1, 2004, can be crowned G4techTV Best of CES. Coverage of CES and the G4techTV Best of CES Awards will air nationally throughout January 2005.<BR><BR>All entries must be received by Dec. 15, 2004. CES exhibitors are encouraged to submit their products to G4techTV for consideration.&nbsp; Visit <A href="http://www.g4techtv.com/bestofces" target=_blank>www.g4techtv.com/bestofces</A> for entry forms and rules.
</span>

